---
/**
 * Privacy page — simple privacy policy for NilaTales.
 * No cookies, no tracking, no personal data collected.
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-06-21';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="NilaTales privacy policy — no cookies, no tracking, no personal data."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16" aria-label="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="font-rounded text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="font-rounded text-sm text-kohl-300 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 font-rounded text-base text-kohl-700 leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">No Tracking</h2>
          <p>NilaTales does not use cookies, analytics, or third-party tracking scripts. We do not collect or store any personal information about you or your children.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">No Accounts</h2>
          <p>This website has no login, no sign-up, and no user accounts. All stories, comics, and activities are freely accessible without registration.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">Local Storage</h2>
          <p>The Bedtime Mode toggle uses a CSS class on the document element — it does not store any data. Your preference is not saved between visits.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">External Resources</h2>
          <p>Google Fonts (Baloo 2, Fraunces, Inter, JetBrains Mono, Noto Tamil) are loaded from Google's CDN. No personal data is sent to Google — only the font file request. If you prefer not to load external fonts, use a browser extension to block third-party requests.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>NilaTales is designed for children ages 3–12. We do not collect any information from children. There are no forms, no comment sections, and no way for a child to submit personal data on this website.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-rounded text-xl font-bold text-kohl-900 mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about privacy? Reach out via the <a href="/about/" class="text-twilight-500 hover:underline">About page</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-paper-300">
        <a href="/" class="btn-clay-primary">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
          Back to stories
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>